-- Aviva Sees Second-Half Restructuring Costs Rising, Posts Loss
-- B y   K e i t h   C a m p b e l l
-- 2012-08-09T06:11:53Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-09/aviva-sees-second-half-restructuring-costs-rising-posts-loss.html
Aviva Plc (AV/)  said it expects
restructuring costs to rise in the second half. The insurer
swung to a first-half loss of 681 million pounds on goodwill
writedowns at its U.S. unit.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Keith Campbell at 
 k.campbell@bloomberg.net  